    • retrieveEntryCriteria

      public DocumentActionEntryCriteriaResponse retrieveEntryCriteria(DocumentRequestType requestType, int id, int majorVersion, int minorVersion, String lifecycleName)
      Retrieve the entry criteria for a user action.
      Parameters:
      requestType - Choose to retrieve values for documents or binders.
      id - The document or binder id field value from which to retrieve available user actions.
      majorVersion - The major version number of the document or binder.
      minorVersion - The minor version number of the document or binder.
      lifecycleName - The lifecycle name__v field value from which to retrieve entry criteria. This is retrieved from the Retrieve User Actions request above.
      Returns:
      DocumentActionEntryCriteriaResponse

      Download Controlled Copy Job Results.
      Parameters:

      jobId - The ID of the job, returned from the original job request. For controlled copy, you can find this ID in the Initiate User Action response.
